            the bigger picture and make smarter decisions.
          </p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="cs-item">
        <a class="cs-link">
          <div class="cs-picture">
            <Image
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321318423-f06f85e504b3?q=80&w=826&h=480&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D"
              alt="IT Support"
              width={413}
              height={240}
              class="cs-img"
            />
          </div>
